headline: Fastenal (FAST) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Fastenal (FAST) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +3.57% and +0.88%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
